Johanne mora oa Zakaria le Elizabetha, e ile ea e-ba moprofeta ha a se a holile. Jehova o ile a re Johanne a rute batho hore Mesia oa tla. Ho e-na le hore a rute ka lisynagogeng le litoropong, o ne a rutela lefeelleng. Batho ba tsoang Jerusalema le Judea ba ne ba tla ho tla rutoa ke Johanne. O ne a re ba lokela ho tlohela ho etsa lintho tse mpe e le hore ba thabise Jehova. Ka mor’a moo, ba bangata ba ile ba tlohela ho etsa lintho tse mpe eaba ba kolobetsoa Nokeng ea Jordane.

Batho ba bangata ba ile ba tla ho Johanne ’me ba re: ‘Re lokela ho etsa’ng e le hore re thabise Molimo?’ Johanne a re ho bona: ‘Haeba u e-na le libaki tse peli, fa motho ea se nang eona e ’ngoe.’ Na oa tseba hore ke hobane’ng ha a ne a cho joalo? Batho ba ne ba rata lintho tseo Johanne a ba rutang tsona. Ba bangata ba ipotsa hore na ebe ke eena Mesia. Eaba o re ho bona: ‘Ho na le ea moholo ho ’na ea tlang. Ke motho ea tlaase haholo ha ke bapisoa le eena. ’Na ke kolobetsa ka metsi, empa eena o kolobetsa ka moea o halalelang.’

BloombergNEF e bolela esale pele kholo ea 30% ea selemo le selemo bakeng sa 'maraka oa lefats'e oa polokelo ea matla ho fihlela ka 2030
Mmaraka oa lefats'e oa polokelo ea matla o tla hola ho isa 58GW/178GWh selemo le selemo ka 2030, ha US le China li emetse 54% ea lisebelisoa tsohle, ho latela bolepi ba BloombergNEF.
Tlaleho ea sehlopha sa H1 2022 Energy Storage Market Outlook e phatlalalitsoe nakoana pele ho bofelong ba Hlakubele. Leha re amohela hore ho romelloa ha nako e haufi ho fokotsehile ke lithibelo tsa phepelo, ho tla ba le sekhahla sa kholo ea selemo le selemo ea 30% 'marakeng, BloombergNEF e boletse esale pele.
BloombergNEF e boetse e hlokometse hore polokelo ea betri ea lithium-ion e kentse letsoho 95% ea matla a macha a ts'ebeliso lefatšeng ka bophara selemong se fetileng, ka "mekhelo e 'maloa feela e sa tloaelehang" joalo ka lits'ebetso tse tharo tse ncha tsa polokelo ea matla a moea naheng ea China tse etsang kakaretso ea 170MW/760MWh.
Feme e lebelletse hore lithium e tla boloka ts'ebetso eo 'marakeng bakeng sa lilemo tse' maloa tse tlang, e lebelletse hore libeteri tsa phallo, li-electrothermal le theknoloji e meng ea nako e telele li ntse li tla lula li lekanyelitsoe ho merero e nyane ea sefofane kapa merero e khethehileng. Leha ho le joalo, nakong e tlang, polokelo ea matla ea nako e telele e ka fana ka matla a feme a se nang mesi ho marang-rang, BloombergNEF e hlokometse.

Ka setso sena se ne se bolela ho tloha ntlheng ea pele ea tlhokomeliso ho ea thekisong, empa lefatšeng la kajeno la kahisano, e fetela hole le moo. Jodi Parker

Mecha ea litaba ea sechaba ke mokhoa o tšoanang le o mong moo o seng le monyetla oa ho rekisa feela, o na le monyetla oa hore bareki ba hau ba o rekisetse! El Tom Collins Ke e 'ngoe ea tsona lino e tummeng ka ho fetisisa New York, e hlahile toropong ena ka 1876, e mo etsang e mong oa balaoli ba tummeng ba bareng ea machabeng e ithorisang ka tse joalo.
Leha ho le joalo, haeba seo u se batlang ke ho natefeloa ke seno sena se entsoeng ka gin ka lilamunu tse bobebe le likhahla tse monate, khutso ea ntlo ea hau le k'hamphani eo u e ratang, ena ke risepe ea etsa lebenkele la Tom Collins ka tsela ya maiketsetso.
Lisebelisoa:
- Li-ounces tse 2
- Hangata 1 ea lero la lemone
- 1 ho fafatsa sirapo
- 1 khalase ea lemone
- Ciliegia e le 1
- Metsi a soda
- Ice
Litokisetso:
- El Tom Collins Ke seno se ka lokisoang ka kotloloho ka khalase.
- Ho etsa sena, ntho ea pele eo u lokelang ho e etsa ke ho tšela gin ka khalase e telele (mofuta oa Collins), ebe u eketsa lero la lemone le sirapo.
- Ebe u eketsa likhalase tse peli kapa tse tharo tsa leqhoa, ebe u tlatsa khalase ka metsi a phatsimang.
- Haeba o batla ho e ts'oara ka mokhoa o tsoetseng pele, o ka khabisa ka khalase ea lemone moeling oa khalase, le cheri e ka hare ho Tom Collins.

Merrimack Valley – O ikutloa a Like Home
Lutse har'a k'honeng leboea-bochabela ho Massachusetts ka Essex County, le Merrimack Valley ke lehae la hoo e ka bang 350,000 baahi. The dikgetho matlo Range ho tloha metseng ea litoropo, loft-style apartments to large, malapeng a se nang balekane-lelapa libakeng tse ka tlaase ho moo tse tsoetseng pele. Empa ke dikgetho ka ho lekaneng hore o teng le baahi ba nakong e tlang? Na e fana ka mefuta-futa ea, theko, sebakeng se le dithusaleago hore baahi ba batla le ho hlokahale?
ho qala ka 2017, le Merrimack Valley Komisi Planning sebelisana le baahi, baahi ba metse, bao e seng phaello, lik'holeje le liunivesithi, ke jwa, profesionalce thekiso ea matlo, le ba nang le seabo e meng ho hlahloba litlhoko tsa ba Merrimack Valley baahi kajeno le kamoo ho ka kopana le litlhoko tsa bona tsa ka holimo ho lilemo tse latelang tse hlano. ha ka ho feletseng, boiteko bo sena se tla fella ka hore 2023 Moralo Merrimack Valley Regional Housing, le khaolo ea motho ka mong e tsepame menyetla matlo le liphephetso ka 15 baahi sebakeng sa.
Re qeta ho ea moo matlo liketsahalo ho pholletsa le Merrimack Valley le di go konosetseng leano likarolo, empa u mema hore u latele re ka metswedi ya dikgang (Facebook le Twitter) ho lula morao-letsatsi ka boemo ba lokolloa ha 2023 Moralo Merrimack Valley Regional Housing. Re lebeletse ka thabo ho sebetsa le uena ho kenya tshebetsong morero oa le etsa bonnete ba hore “Merrimack Valley Feels Like Home.”

Phuthiatsana
Phuthiatsana is a community council located in the Berea District of Lesotho. Its population in 2006 was 25,660.[3]
Villages[edit]
The community of Phuthiatsana includes the villages of Cana, Ha Bose, Ha Bulara, Ha Chaba, Ha Hlaonyane, Ha Jane, Ha Kholopane, Ha Koone, Ha Korotsoane, Ha Kotita, Ha Lebina, Ha Lechesa, Ha Lehana, Ha Lenea, Ha Lenea (Ha Mamathe), Ha Libenyane, Ha Mahleke, Ha Majara, Ha Malesela, Ha Mamathe, Ha Matelile, Ha Matseleli, Ha Moepi, Ha Mokhathi, Ha Mokhehle, Ha Mokhethi, Ha Mokoma, Ha Molala, Ha Monnanyane, Ha Morolong, Ha Mosethe, Ha Mosobela, Ha Mosoeunyane, Ha Motsoaole, Ha Motsora, Ha Mphetlane, Ha Mphunyetsane, Ha Ntebele, Ha Ntsabane, Ha Ntsang, Ha Ntsenki, Ha Patso, Ha Phalatsane, Ha Phiri, Ha Phoofolo, Ha Ramachine, Ha Ramotete, Ha Rankali, Ha Rankhalile (Likocheng), Ha Rantung, Ha Rapalo, Ha Rapopo, Ha Seele, Ha Selone, Ha Seoka, Ha Sepiriti (Moterong), Ha Seutloali, Ha Taeke (Liphakoeng), Ha Thaka-Mpholo, Ha Thube, Ha Tjobe, Ha Tšekelo, Ha Tšepo, Ha Tšoeunyane, Hlokoa-Le-Mafi, Khafung, Khalahali, Kolone, Koti-sephola, Lipatolong, Liphiring, Mafikeng, Mahlanyeng, Majaheng, Malieleng, Mamathe, Masoeling, Mohlakeng, Paballong, Phuthing, Sebala-Bala, Sefateng, Thota-Peli, Tilimaneng and Tsila-Tsila.[4]

Kenya go khatisa go mekgwa e mengwe ya lipapali tsa WhatsApp mo puong ya Sesotho ka mekgwa e mengwe. Kenya go šetše, gabane, le kgobokanyetsa le batho ba ba na le karolwana le wena. Kwalwa tša ho hlahella mokhoa oa ho bua le mokhoa oa ho etsa lintho le ho emela sefahleho sa hau ho mohlabanyana oa hau ho batho ba ba ba sa le tšatši ka puong ya hau. Tsoha ka ho ya ka tokelo ea hao ka ho bokaha lipontšo tsa tlase tsa ho etsa karolwana le tšehetso ya hao. Swotšha lefatshe la dikgakgolo tsa WhatsApp mo Sepedi ho feta diphetho tša boleng. Kena, thusa le go nna le labogedi le le bolokaneng mo moetapele wa hau.

Leseli le khanyang la LED (Horticultural Lighting)
NLeseli tsa ew tse ikhethang maboneng a temo le ho nts'etsapele letoto la lihlahisoa tsa linaleli tse lumellanang le litlhoko tsa kholo tsa indasteri le tsa bolulo. Mabone a temo a boetse a tsejoa e le khanya ea lebone kapa lebone la semela, tse sebelisoang haholo molemong oa ho hola ka tlung, joalo ka tamati e holang kapa se monate matlong a polokelo. Mabone a hola ka ho fetesisa a LED e ka ba phepelo e ntle kapa tlatsetso ea mabone a letsatsi bakeng sa limela, tseo ntle le ho ba le matla a phahameng a matla, li hlokang ho ba le mohloli o felletseng oa leseli o etselitsoeng ho ts'ehetsa kholo ea semela. Re fana ka lisebelisoa tse holang tsa matla a holimo joalo ka kotulo kapa letoto le holang habonolo, leo e ka bang khanya ea 400w, 600w le 1000w watt. Haeba u khetha khanya e nyane haholo, re boetse re na le lebone la kholo la UFO kapa Moroallo oa 100watt, 150watt le 200watt. Bakeng sa lishelefo tsa hydroponic, re boetse re na le T5 LED e hola leseli le T8 LED tube bakeng sa ho hola. Haeba u lebisa tlhokomelo serapeng sa lapeng, tleloubu ea lebone la E26 e ka ba khetho e ntle eo re ka fanang ka eona. HAINING Xinguangyuan Lighting ke moetsi ea hloahloa oa LED grow Lightin China. Re fana ka lits'ebeletso tsa OEM bakeng sa lihlahisoa tse etellang pele tsa mabone a LED. HAINING Xinguangyuan Lighting ke moetsi oa Leseli la ho Hlahisa Leseli le moetsi oa mabone a LED.

Shanghai Dunke Machining Co, Ltd., e thehiloe ka 2004, e bohareng ba Toropo ea Fengcheng, Setereke sa Fengxian, Shanghai. Ke feela koloi e nkang metsotso e 15 ho tloha Shanghai FTA bakeng sa Mechini e Meholo. Feme e akaretsa sebaka sa 22000 m2, moo sebaka sa tlhahiso se leng 11000 m2. Feme e na le bahlahisi ba litsebi ba 98 le baetsi ba boenjiniere, le lisebelisoa tse fetang 80 tsa lisebelisoa tsa tlhahiso, tseo boholo ba tsona e leng lisebelisoa tsa mochini oa CNC. Khamphani e fetisitse tiiso ea ISO 9001: 2015 ea tsamaiso ea boleng ba machaba ka 2018. Khamphani e nkile nako e telele e tšoarehile indastering ea hydraulic mme e bokelletse lilemo tse ngata tsa boiphihlelo phetisong ea hydraulic ho fa bareki litheko tse felletseng tsa litharollo tsa mahlale a hydraulic.
